# Pionersky, Yermekeyevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Pionersky () is a rural locality (a selo) in Spartaksky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 220 as of 2010. There is 1 street.
Geography
Pionersky is located 15&nbsp;km southeast of Yermekeyevo (the district's administrative centre) by road. Spartak is the nearest rural locality.
